skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: nutrition info
des: Nutrition info is an alexa skill that will tell you nutritive value of food like how much calories one banana contains, nutrients in one egg. You just have to say alexa ask nutrition info, then alexa will give you warm welcome and tell what you can do with this skill. Then you just have to say nutrients in one banana or calories in one coffee. Try with any food item and check nutrition value in just couple of seconds.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
